OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FI am flying tomorrow to Evian in
OL,7,FFrance with the prime minister for
OL,8,Fwhat will be the most surreal summit
OL,9,Fof world leaders of my and his career.
OL,11,FAnd that is because Keir Starmer's
OL,12,Ftenure as prime minister is
OL,13,Fconditional on whether Andy Burnham
OL,14,Fbecomes a Labour MP on Friday and then
OL,15,Fhow fast he moves to unseat the PM.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
