OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FStarmer and his ministers do their
OL,7,Fbest in public to pretend that they
OL,8,Fare governing as normal. In private,
OL,9,Fhis colleagues are explicit that he is
OL,10,Fin limbo, unable to have confidence
OL,11,Fthat he will remain PM for many weeks
OL,12,For even days longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FSo, although this summit of the
OL,7,Fleaders of the G7 richest economies
OL,8,Fhas an important agenda - re-opening
OL,9,Fand policing the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,10,Freinforcing support for Ukraine,
OL,11,Freducing European AI dependence on the
OL,12,FUS (so graphically manifest in
OL,13,FWashington's order to Anthropic to
OL,14,Fshut down Fable) - none of the leaders
OL,15,Fknow if Starmer is there as the now-
OL,16,Fand-future PM or a temporary caretaker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FThe PM has said that he will fight
OL,7,FBurnham if he launches a leadership
OL,8,Fchallenge. But his cabinet colleagues
OL,9,Ftell me they don't know if that is
OL,10,Fwhat he feels he has to say, to
OL,11,Fmaintain a semblance of authority, or
OL,12,Fwhether he means it.
OL,14,FOne minister tells me the prime
OL,15,Fminister would lose badly in a head-to-
OL,16,Fhead contest against Burnham. "He
OL,17,Fwould be humiliated" said the
OL,18,Fminister. "He has been told that.
OL,19,FWhether he believes it is another
OL,20,Fthing."
OL,26,@xD@_OUyD@TO]zD@KOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
