CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FAnother minister says the mortal blow
OL,7,Fwas the resignation as defence
OL,8,Fsecretary, John Healey. Before Healey
OL,9,Frevealed himself to be unwilling to
OL,10,Fserve a PM unable to find the money
OL,11,Fdeemed necessary by Healey to mend the
OL,12,FUK's overstretched defences, ministers
OL,13,Fwere reluctantly rallying around
OL,14,FStarmer. No longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
