PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,F"What was half-hearted support for the
OL,7,FPM has more-or-less gone," said the
OL,8,Fminister. "He could try to replace
OL,9,Fthose ministers he feels have been
OL,10,Fmost disrespectful to him, like Ed
OL,11,FMiliband and Shabana Mahmood, but that
OL,12,Fwould probably be the final nail in
OL,13,Fhis own coffin."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@ZO]pD@KOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
