PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FStarmer is seen as isolated from most
OL,7,Fof his colleagues, seeking solace and
OL,8,Fadvice from his attorney general
OL,9,FRichard Hermer and his former chief of
OL,10,Fstaff, Morgan McSweeney - whose
OL,11,Finformal return to the centre of
OL,12,Fgovernment alienates many Labour MPs,
OL,13,Fbecause of his central role in the
OL,14,Fdebacle of Peter Mandelson's stint as
OL,15,FBritish ambassador in Washington.
OL,17,FThis period in purgatory will stretch
OL,18,Fthrough this week, but ministers
OL,19,Fbelieve the moment of Starmer's fall
OL,20,For redemption will be next weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781470070
OL,3,CIs the PM about to attend his last
OL,4,Csummit of world leaders?
OL,6,FIf Burnham wins decisively in
OL,7,FMakerfield, reversing the seemingly
OL,8,Fdecisive shift to Reform of the local
OL,9,Felections just a few weeks ago,
OL,10,Fministers expect that Labour MPs will
OL,11,Fwant an orderly transition from
OL,12,FStarmer to Burnham, without the chaos
OL,13,Fand uncertainty of a lengthy contested
OL,14,Fleadership election.
OL,16,FBurnham and Starmer will therefore
OL,17,Fengage in a political dance, assessing
OL,18,Fhow far the other will go to take the
OL,19,Fparty to the brink of that messy
OL,20,Fcontest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
